    <div class="summary">
        <h3><a href="/questions/8785/var-calculation-covariance-matrix-is-not-positive-semidefinite" class="question-hyperlink">VaR Calculation - Covariance matrix is not positive semidefinite</a></h3>
        <div class="excerpt">
            This is a basic question.

I have three assets, equally weighted, and all the mutual covariances are -1. Then, the covariance matrix looks like - 

...
